@ description: Sweet spot / threshold development session
@ equipment: bike, power meter, HR strap

# Threshold Ride [Cycling] (2026-03-09) @RPE 7
@ location: Indoor trainer

- Warmup 15min @60% FTP
- 5x:
  - Bike 5min @95% FTP
  - Recover 3min @50% FTP
- Cooldown 10min @Z1

> Felt strong through set 3, faded on 4 and 5.
> Next time try 4x6min instead of 5x5min.
